            <c id="ref15" level="file">
               <did>
                  <unittitle>Posters</unittitle>
               </did>
               <scopecontent id="aspace_d242d17c6158187a9588fdf41ce1f926">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Includes posters created by the Palestinian Liberation Organization (PLO) and Roots (a Palestinian youth group that was based in Washington, D.C., in the 1980s) depicting movement martyrs: Abu Jihad, Abu Muhammad, Abu al-Hawl, Abu Iyad, Khalid al-Hasan, Muhammad Ismail Abu Nafisah, Husni Abd al-Rahman al-Araj, and commemorating Land Day; PLO anniversaries; and the 1989 Intifada.</p>
               </scopecontent>
